<style>
.visor {
    background-color: rgba(250,250,250,0.3);
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
}
.visor .container {
    max-width: 600px;
}
.visor .container p {
    text-align: justify;
}
</style>

<div class='visor'>
    <div class='container'>
        <p>Select an Agency from the dropdown to administrate for. If the desired agency is not listed, then the currently logged in user does not have the required permissions to coordinate for that agency.</p>
        <br>
        <select class="agencySelect form-control input-lg select" onchange={{action (mut agencyId) value="target.value"}}>
            <option>Select An Agency</option>
            {{#each agencies as |agencyChoice|}}
            <option selected={{eq agency agencyChoice}} value={{agencyChoice.id}}>{{agencyChoice.name}}</option>
            {{/each}}
        </select>
        <br>
        {{#link-to 'agency.detail' agencyId class='btn btn-primary btn-lg button-pos'}}
            <!--<button type='button' class='btn btn-primary btn-lg button-pos'>View Grants</button>-->
            View Grants
        {{/link-to}}
        <p>If the currently logged in user does not have the correct permissions, he or she may request those permissions from the Agency's administration.</p>
    </div>
</div>
